<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="glory-n">glory <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɡlɔːri/    美 /'ɡlɔːri/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>光荣；荣誉</strong></h4>
<p>fame or honour that you get for achieving sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>return with glory
凯旋</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She dreamt of future glory as an Olympic champion.
她梦想将来能得到奥运冠军的荣誉。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>荣耀的事；可赞颂的事物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The temple is one of the glories of ancient Greece.
这座庙宇是古希腊的一大荣耀。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>壮丽；壮观；辉煌：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The house has now been restored to its <strong>former glory</strong>.
现在这栋房子又恢复了它往日的辉煌。</p></div></div>